  "description": {
    "zh": "嘿，伙计，我的朋友们显然在搞什么事情。上次你刚干完那些Scav的时候，他们几乎立刻就给我打了电话，你想想，他们可能正在搞些娱乐活动，打赌啊，搞钱什么的。长话短说，他们又来让你去屠Scav了，但是这次要用老伙计AKS-74U。我不是特别想知道他们在整什么花样，但是他们给了很高的价钱，考虑一下？",
    "en": "Hey there, man. Well, my friends are clearly up to something. Last time you dropped some Scavs, they called me almost instantly, and, you know, it seemed like they had a bit of entertainment going on. Making bets, making cash. Long story short, they want you to decimate Scavs again, but this time on Customs and using a good old AKS-74U. I don't really want to know what kind of show they are making of it, but they offer some top cash. So, you in?"
  },
